Home page

Live Play:

Click live button, go to join live. Filemaker starts live, open and close game.
  |
  |___if live and open, no move, user is the leader, set by Filemaker
  |
  |___if live and open, has move, user is follower
  |       |
  |       |___post player name, Filemaker set player ID, latest move
  |
  |___If not live or not open, "say please check back again."


